Subject: Re: [PATCH] PC-9800 subarch. support for 2.5.62-AC1 (6/21) FS & partiton
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
